ygData.messageBody:
Cool! Thanks for sharing. :-)
I have a few books on names. and the dictionary is fun to look through. I
found my cleric's last name in a medical dictionary. I also found a
seemingly innocent sounding first name that means something pretty gross.
luv,
-Su
